{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"compacted_at":1783077610441058001,"compiled_state":{"alias":"seedy-edema-groan","assignee":null,"author":"Joe Oakhart","bridge_alerts":[],"comments":[{"author":"Joe Oakhart","body":"FORCE_CLOSE: close gate(s) bypassed by user approval — no completion/signature attestation was signed. Reason: \"Item 13 (config/reconcile/editor/batch_dispatch splits) merged to main via Gerrit 218-221.\". Session: 6b6d88059.","timestamp":1783077608677035001}],"created_at":1783056815137117001,"deps":[],"description":"# Size: split config.py + extract reconcile _run_differs + proactively split near-cap files\n\n## What\n- `config.py` (1310): extract the dataclass/schema from the env/CLI-override + cache machinery along the existing seam; collapse the `_SECTIONS` vs per-class dual source of truth where feasible.\n- `reconcile.py` (1485): extract the `_run_differs` phase (382 LOC) into a sibling `run_differs.py` along the phase seam the sequencer already carves.\n- Proactively split the 8 files within 25 LOC of the cap along their named seams (editor `_Handler`, batch_dispatch per-ticket dispatch, transition `transition_compute` — see item 12, etc.).\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] config.py under cap (or materially reduced) with the schema extracted; no behavior change (config tests green).\n- [ ] `_run_differs` lives in a sibling module; reconcile.py reduced; reconciler suites green.\n- [ ] At least the top near-cap growers split along real seams (no <100-LOC fragments).\n- [ ] `make lint` + full suite green; commit(s) carry `rebar-ticket:` trailers.","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[["parent","9322-f84a-e047-4471"]],"parent_id":"9322-f84a-e047-4471","parent_status_uuid":"2b1dbbea-24ac-4bb7-8e3c-c08e9fa17a70","preconditions_summary":{"status":"pre-manifest"},"priority":1,"reverts":[],"signature":null,"status":"closed","tags":[],"ticket_id":"b043-94